ðŸ—ï¸ Data Selection and Filtering Functions

1ï¸âƒ£ `loc[]` â€“ label-based selection  
2ï¸âƒ£ `iloc[]` â€“ position-based selection  
3ï¸âƒ£ `at[]` and `iat[]` â€“ fast scalar access  
4ï¸âƒ£ `isin()` â€“ filter by list of values  
5ï¸âƒ£ `query()` â€“ filter using expression

# Example
print("Select 'Name' column:\n", df['Name'])
print("Select first row:\n", df.iloc[0])
print("Select rows where Age > 28:\n", df[df['Age'] > 28])
print("Check if Age in [25, 35]:\n", df[df['Age'].isin([25, 35])])

